#. Tag: term
#: deployment_prep_power.xml:44
#, no-c-format
msgid "Supported servers"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: deployment_prep_power.xml:46
#, no-c-format
msgid "Check the database of &suse;-certified hardware to make sure that your particular hardware configuration is supported. The database is available at <link xlink:href=\"https://www.suse.com/yessearch/Search.jsp\"/> . &productname; may support additional IBM &power; systems that are not listed. For the latest information, refer to the IBM Information Center for Linux at <link xlink:href=\"https://www.ibm.com/support/knowledgecenter/linuxonibm/liaam/liaamdistros.htm\"/> ."
