#: deployment_prep_power.xml:76
#, no-c-format
msgid "Hard disk requirements"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: deployment_prep_power.xml:78
#, no-c-format
msgid "The disk requirements depend on the type of installation selected and the usage scenario. Normally, a properly working system requires more space than the installation itself. The minimum requirements are as follows."
